videos.description: Kyle Guy knocks down the 3-pointer as the shot clock is running down, then on the next play, Jay Huff blocks the much taller Christ Koumadje.
videos.headline: Huff follows Guy's 3 with block

videos.description: Virginia's Kyle Guy doesn't miss a 3-point attempt during the entire first half, ending it with 2 tough fadeaway 3-pointers to put Virginia up big.
videos.headline: Guy ends the half with 2 difficult 3-pointers

videos.description: Mamadi Diakite misses the jumper but gets the ball back and dunks with authority.
videos.headline: Diakite throws down the dunk for Virginia
